OL,3,CNova Twins on MOBOs, defining their
OL,4,Csound and 'kicking down doors'
OL,6,FThere's a connection between Amy Love
OL,7,Fand Georgia South that could only come
OL,8,Fthrough years of friendship.
OL,10,FManufactured musical partnerships
OL,11,Fsimply can't replicate the bond forged
OL,12,Fby hours of shared childhood
OL,13,Fexperience.
OL,15,FKnown as Nova Twins - spoiler, they
OL,16,Faren't actually twins - Love and South
OL,17,Fgravitated towards each other in their
OL,18,Fearly years.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
