CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774541484
OL,3,CNova Twins on MOBOs, defining their
OL,4,Csound and 'kicking down doors'
OL,6,F"We met through my brother," Georgia
OL,7,Fsays, "because Amy and him went to
OL,8,Fcollege together. We were just
OL,9,Finseparable growing up.
OL,11,F"We hung out all the time and one day,
OL,12,Fwe were like 'shall we write a song
OL,13,Ftogether?"
OL,15,FThey've since released three albums,
OL,16,Ftheir latest, Parasites & Butterflies
OL,17,Fcame out last year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
