OL,3,CNova Twins on MOBOs, defining their
OL,4,Csound and 'kicking down doors'
OL,6,FThrow in a Mercury Prize nomination
OL,7,Ffor their second album, Supernova, and
OL,8,Fyou might think it's been all plain
OL,9,Fsailing for the pair...but they've
OL,10,Ffaced a hurdle or two.
OL,12,FAmy says their sound is "a big mix of
OL,13,Frock, R&B, hip-hop, electronic and
OL,14,Fgrime".
OL,16,F"We just make all these crazy sounds
OL,17,Fand we use our whole bodies, that
OL,18,Fwhole energy to create that genre
OL,19,Fclash," she adds.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774541484
OL,3,CNova Twins on MOBOs, defining their
OL,4,Csound and 'kicking down doors'
OL,6,F"I think we felt free creating music",
OL,7,FGeorgia adds. "Both growing up in
OL,8,Fmulti-heritage homes, it was just so
OL,9,Fnatural to blend different genres,
OL,10,Flike how we would blend different food
OL,11,For fashion."
OL,13,FHowever, upon entering the music
OL,14,Findustry they were met with many
OL,15,Fquestioning what 'box' to put them in.
OL,17,FGeorgia remembers, "We were just
OL,18,Fthinking, we're heavy, we're
OL,19,Fdifferent, just put us in rock, or
OL,20,Fhowever you'd place any heavy band
OL,21,Fwith loads of amps and a loud drum kit.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774541484
OL,3,CNova Twins on MOBOs, defining their
OL,4,Csound and 'kicking down doors'
OL,6,F"That wasn't the case, because we
OL,7,Fdidn't look how rock bands look, that
OL,8,Fwas the main challenge, but we've been
OL,9,Fknocking down doors."
OL,11,FThe Nova Twins tell ITV News' Rishi
OL,12,FDavda how, coming from multi-heritage
OL,13,Fhomes, it was 'so natural' to them to
OL,14,Fblend so many genres and influences
OL,15,Finto their music
OL,17,FFormed back in 2014, maybe the box
OL,18,Fthey fit into is that box that says
OL,19,F"we don't fit in any of the other
OL,20,Fboxes".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
