OL,3,CNova Twins on MOBOs, defining their
OL,4,Csound and 'kicking down doors'
OL,6,FTheir musical direction received a
OL,7,Fweighty seal of approval in 2023. Sir
OL,8,FElton John said: "these girls rock my
OL,9,Fworld...they are just for me
OL,10,Fphenomenal."
OL,12,FNova Twins have supported the likes of
OL,13,FMuse, Foo Fighters and Lenny Kravitz
OL,14,Fon tour.
OL,16,FThis summer, as well as performing at
OL,17,FAll Points East and Rock in Rio,
OL,18,Fthey'll be opening for American
OL,19,Frockers Evanescence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
