OL,3,CNova Twins on MOBOs, defining their
OL,4,Csound and 'kicking down doors'
OL,6,FInterviews always gently encourage
OL,7,Freflection and recollection and both
OL,8,FLove and South have fond memories of
OL,9,Fthe MOBO awards.
OL,11,FFounded by Kanya King and Andy Ruffell
OL,12,Fin 1996, the awards celebrate music of
OL,13,Fblack origin - with 2026 marking its
OL,14,F30th anniversary.
OL,16,FDestiny's Child, Rihanna, Tina Turner,
OL,17,FJay-Z, Lauryn Hill, Chaka Khan, Usher,
OL,18,FSade, Stormzy, Little Simz, Raye, the
OL,19,Flist of some previous MOBO performers
OL,20,Freads like potentially the greatest
OL,21,Ffestival line up ever.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
