OL,3,CNova Twins on MOBOs, defining their
OL,4,Csound and 'kicking down doors'
OL,6,FLooking at Georgia, Amy says: "I
OL,7,Fremember watching the MOBOs on your
OL,8,Fliving room floor. We would always
OL,9,Fdream and think 'one day we're going
OL,10,Fto play that'."
OL,12,FThey did in fact play at the awards
OL,13,Flast year.
OL,15,F"To create a scene for black music and
OL,16,Fblack culture, it's a movement that
OL,17,Fcontributes to this country so much.
OL,18,FRevenue, culturally and just like
OL,19,Fgeneral memories and happiness. It's
OL,20,Fincredible."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
