OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774541484
OL,3,CNova Twins on MOBOs, defining their
OL,4,Csound and 'kicking down doors'
OL,6,FGeorgia South and Amy Love look back
OL,7,Fon how they watched the MOBO awards at
OL,8,Fhome dreaming of one day playing at
OL,9,Fthe ceremony
OL,11,FTwo-time Brit Award nominees, Nova
OL,12,FTwins have had their own part to play
OL,13,Fin the history and legacy of the MOBO
OL,14,Fawards.
OL,16,FBack in 2020, they posted on social
OL,17,Fmedia calling on organisers to
OL,18,Fintroduce a category that could
OL,19,Fincorporate their genre of music.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
