OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774541484
OL,3,CNova Twins on MOBOs, defining their
OL,4,Csound and 'kicking down doors'
OL,6,FFor many years the focus had been on
OL,7,Fsoul, reggae, R&B, grime and hip-hop.
OL,8,FThere wasn't really a space for rock
OL,9,Fmusic.
OL,11,FThe higher-ups quickly took note of
OL,12,FLove and South's open letter and
OL,13,Flooked into it.
OL,15,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
