OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1774541484
OL,3,CNova Twins on MOBOs, defining their
OL,4,Csound and 'kicking down doors'
OL,6,FJump to 2022 and the introduction of
OL,7,Fthe Best Alternative Music Act trophy,
OL,8,Fsomething Nova Twins were nominated
OL,9,Ffor both its debut year and this year,
OL,10,F2026.
OL,12,FSouth says, "when we thought about it,
OL,13,Fthere wasn't actually a category for
OL,14,Fheavier music out there. Sister
OL,15,FRosetta Tharpe was the first person to
OL,16,Finnovate rock music, so it makes sense
OL,17,Fthat we celebrate all genres of music
OL,18,Fof black origin".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
